== Consonants ==
{| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center;"
|+ Standard West Frisian consonants<ref>Based on the consonant table in {{Harvcoltxt|Sipma|1913|p=8}}. The allophones {{IPA|[ɲ, ɡ, β̞]}} are not included.</ref>{{sfnp|Hoekstra|2001|p=84}}
